```{r}
library(readxl)
all_data <- read_excel("all_data.xlsx")
View(all_data)
```
Primitive R Code to Take a look at variables. 

```{r cars}
covid <- all_data
x = covid$Percent_Urban
y = covid$Lethality_Rate
cor(x,y)
plot(x ~y)
```



```{r pressure, echo=FALSE}
model <- lm(x~y)
summary(model)
```
